 Since moodle processed the upload, the file got stored on the file system, and the instructor could see it.Â  Yet Moodle didn't log a sumission for this student (in the mdl_log or mdl_assignment_submission tables). Of course this all relates to a bigger issue, which I hope is better in Moodle 2.x.Â Â Â  Moodle needs to do a better job of handling session (and auth token) timeouts that are discovered in the middle of an operation.Â Â Â  It has come up before in the tracker. http://tracker.moodle.org/browse/MDL-11972 Best, -Garret
